  "title": "ASSISTANT MANAGER",
  "description": "<p>Assistant restaurant managers oversee and support the operations at dining establishments to ensure profitability and an enjoyable dining experience. These professionals work in conjunction with restaurant managers.</p>\n<p>* Opening and closing the resaurants.</p>\n<p>* Recruiting , induction and mentoring of new staff members.</p>\n<p>* Scheduling shifts and assigning tables to waitstaff.</p>\n<p>* Resolving customer's questions and grievances in a professional manner.</p>\n<p>* Conducting payroll activities in an accurate and timely manner.</p>\n<p>* Ensuring that the restaurant adheres to pertinent health and safety regulations.</p>\n<p>* Purcahsing new ingredients, kitchen utensils and equipments as stock is depleted or damaged.</p>\n<p>* Sourcing better deals on all resources and equipments that warrant replacing or replenishment.</p>\n<p>* Recording all income and expenses and ensuring that cash registers are balanced.</p>",
